(14, 'Sega considering Netflix-like game subscription service - BBC.com', 12, 11, '<div\r\n  data-component=\"text-block\"\r\n  class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"\r\n  style=\"\r\n    margin: 0px auto 16px;\r\n    padding: 0px;\r\n    border: 0px;\r\n    font: inherit;\r\n    vertical-align: baseline;\r\n    position: relative;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    gap: 16px;\r\n    width: 722px;\r\n  \"\r\n>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    Sega is considering launching its own Netflix-like subscription service for\r\n    video games, a move which would accelerate gaming\'s transition towards\r\n    streaming.\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    There are already a number of similar services on the market - such as Xbox\r\n    Game Pass and PlayStation Plus - which see gamers pay a monthly fee for\r\n    access to a range of titles rather than owning them outright.\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    Sega\'s president Shuji Utsumi told the BBC such subscription products were\r\n    \"very interesting\", and his firm was \"evaluating some opportunities\".\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    \"We\'re thinking something - and discussing something - we cannot disclose\r\n    right now,\" he said.\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    Some in the industry have expressed concern about the move however telling\r\n    the BBC it could see gamers \"shelling out more money\" on multiple\r\n    subscription services.\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.36px\"\r\n      >It is not just Sony and Microsoft who offer game subscriptions - there\r\n      are now countless players in the space, with rivals such as Nintendo, EA\r\n      and Ubisoft all offering their own membership plans.</span\r\n    >\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.36px\"><br /></span>\r\n  </p>\r\n  <p\r\n    class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      text-align: center;\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-style: inherit;\r\n      font-variant: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: 18px;\r\n      line-height: 26px;\r\n      font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n      letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <img\r\n      src=\"data:image/webp;base64,\"\r\n      data-filename=\"b1a19f00-bd4f-11ef-8889-ebba28ecef92.png.webp\"\r\n      style=\"width: 100%; float: none\"\r\n    /><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.36px\"><br /></span>\r\n  </p>\r\n  <div\r\n    data-component=\"text-block\"\r\n    class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      margin: 0px auto 16px;\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: medium;\r\n      line-height: inherit;\r\n      font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      gap: 16px;\r\n      width: 722px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Currently, various Sega games are available across multiple streaming\r\n      services.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      The amount these services individually charge vary depending on the\r\n      features and games made available. For example, Xbox Game Pass prices\r\n      range from £6.99 to £14.99 a month, while PlayStation Plus ranges from\r\n      £6.99 to £13.49 a month.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      So it would make financial sense for Sega for people who are playing its\r\n      titles to pay it subscription fees rather its rivals.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      It could also be attractive for people who mostly want to play Sega games\r\n      - but for everyone else it could result in higher costs.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Rachel Howie streams herself playing games on Twitch, where she is known\r\n      as DontRachQuit to her fans, and said she was \"excited and worried\" about\r\n      another subscription service\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"We have so many subscriptions already that we find it very difficult to\r\n      justify signing up for a new one,\" she told the BBC.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"I think that SEGA will definitely have a core dedicated audience that\r\n      will benefit from this, but will the average gamer choose this over\r\n      something like Game Pass?\"\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      And Sophie Smart, Production Director at UK developer No More Robots,\r\n      agreed.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"As someone whose first console was the Sega Mega Drive, what I\'d love\r\n      more than anything is to see Sega thriving and this feels like a step in a\r\n      modern direction,\" she said.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      But she wondered if Sega did create a rival subscription service if this\r\n      would lead to their games being removed from other services.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"If so, it could mean that consumers are shelling out more money across\r\n      owning multiple subscription services,\" she said.\r\n    </p>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div\r\n    data-component=\"subheadline-block\"\r\n    class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 eeiVGB\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      margin: 24px auto 16px;\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: medium;\r\n      line-height: inherit;\r\n      font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      gap: 16px;\r\n      width: 722px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <h2\r\n      class=\"sc-518485e5-0 kRvAla\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        margin-top: 0px;\r\n        margin-bottom: 0px;\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 32px;\r\n        line-height: 36px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.32px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Bringing Sega back\r\n    </h2>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div\r\n    data-component=\"text-block\"\r\n    class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 dlWCEZ\"\r\n    style=\"\r\n      margin: 0px auto 16px;\r\n      padding: 0px;\r\n      border: 0px;\r\n      font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n      font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n      font-stretch: inherit;\r\n      font-size: medium;\r\n      line-height: inherit;\r\n      font-family: \'Times New Roman\';\r\n      font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n      font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n      font-kerning: inherit;\r\n      font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n      font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n      vertical-align: baseline;\r\n      position: relative;\r\n      display: grid;\r\n      gap: 16px;\r\n      width: 722px;\r\n    \"\r\n  >\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Shuji Utsumi spoke to the BBC ahead of the premiere of the film Sonic 3 on\r\n      Saturday, after a year in which he oversaw the launch of Metaphor:\r\n      ReFantazio, Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth, and the latest Sonic the\r\n      Hedgehog game.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Our conversation started in an unexpected way.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      The very first thing Mr Utsumi said to me seemed to suggest that the firm,\r\n      which dominated gaming in the 1990s with a rivalry between Sonic the\r\n      Hedgehog and Nintendo\'s Super Mario, may have lost its way.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"I want to make Sega really shiny again,\" he said.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      He said Sega had been putting too much focus on domestic success in Japan,\r\n      and needed to re-establish itself on a global stage, which would mean\r\n      expanding past its base.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"Sega has been somehow losing confidence,\" he said.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"But why? Sega has a great RPG group, Sega has amazing IPs, Sega is a\r\n      really well-known brand.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"So I was like, hey, now is not the time to be defensive - but more\r\n      offensive.\"\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      He said the company was too concerned about controlling costs when he took\r\n      over, and he wants to \"bring a rock and roll mentality\" to gaming.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      When I told him that sounded familiar - Sega\'s marketing in the 90s often\r\n      tried to position Sonic the Hedgehog as the cool alternative to Mario - he\r\n      agreed.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-style: inherit;\r\n        font-variant: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      <img\r\n        src=\"data:image/webp;base64,\"\r\n        data-filename=\"66d08670-bd50-11ef-8889-ebba28ecef92.jpg.webp\"\r\n        style=\"width: 100%; float: none\"\r\n      />\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      He said the firm now simply must \"make a great game\" in the series.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"The next one is going to be a quite challenging, quite exciting game that\r\n      we are working on,\" he said.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      But he would not divulge whether Sega was considering a follow up to the\r\n      much-loved Sonic Adventure series.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"Sonic Adventure was kind of a game-changer for Sonic,\" he said.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      \"When we release it, it should be good, it should be impressive - we need\r\n      to meet or even exceed people\'s expectations, so it takes some time.\"\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Part of the series which fans have been clamouring to see return is the\r\n      Chao Garden - a much-loved virtual pet synonymous with Sonic Adventure.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p\r\n      class=\"sc-eb7bd5f6-0 fYAfXe\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n        padding: 0px;\r\n        border: 0px;\r\n        font-variant-numeric: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-east-asian: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-alternates: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-position: inherit;\r\n        font-variant-emoji: inherit;\r\n        font-stretch: inherit;\r\n        font-size: 18px;\r\n        line-height: 26px;\r\n        font-family: \'BBC Reith Serif\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\r\n        font-optical-sizing: inherit;\r\n        font-size-adjust: inherit;\r\n        font-kerning: inherit;\r\n        font-feature-settings: inherit;\r\n        font-variation-settings: inherit;\r\n        vertical-align: baseline;\r\n        color: rgb(32, 34, 36);\r\n        letter-spacing: -0.36px;\r\n      \"\r\n    >\r\n      Mr Utsumi said \"we\'ve been talking about it\" - but would not go into\r\n      further detail, only that he could not \"say too much about it\".\r\n    </p>\r\n    <div\r\n      data-component=\"subheadline-block\"\r\n      class=\"sc-18fde0d6-0 eeiVGB\"\r\n      style=\"\r\n       